{"title":"1920春·陈望道","authors":["方竟成"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":7,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"1920春·陈望道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方竟成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1919年太不平静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，义乌分水塘初春夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又太平静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几声狗吠，一钩月牙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溪水凉凉地流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这太平静与"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太不平静之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是年轻陈望道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独坐柴屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛然翻开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个叫马克思的大胡子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写的《共产党宣言》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅称你“这一仗总算打胜了”的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一师风潮”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又在耳边呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“五四”的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然逼退了军警的枪刺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要动摇和摒弃旧制度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“改良实施都是劳而无益”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿芙乐尔巡洋舰的炮声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"划破了冬宫的统治"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀铁锤迸发出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毫不迟疑的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸碎锁链"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧枯拉朽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是根本的解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块铺板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两条长凳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一盏油灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孜孜不倦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈望道在一页一页翻译"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平静的柴屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于无声处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇聚着中国共产主义的火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，柔和的晨光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从柴屋木窗流进来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舔拂着平静入睡的陈望道和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他手上的最后一页文稿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整一个春季"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少次手足冻麻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个耿耿难眠之夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于诞生了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《共产党宣言》第一部中文本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1920年春天的陈望道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样离开了老母亲煮的菜饭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开了故乡分水塘的柴屋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀揣着新火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追踪着新朝阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大步向前去"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}